539
00:36:16,218 --> 00:36:18,366
Sure, send me the location. I'll go now.

540
00:36:19,858 --> 00:36:21,650
A family intends to adopt her.

541
00:36:21,730 --> 00:36:23,185
It's a good thing.

542
00:36:23,895 --> 00:36:26,376
However, I'm not sure about Xiao Wei.

543
00:36:27,178 --> 00:36:30,868
During this period, I can tell
that she trusts you guys a lot.

544
00:36:31,626 --> 00:36:33,526
