please contact us again.

549
00:36:47,433 --> 00:36:48,798
Sure, no problem.

550
00:36:48,878 --> 00:36:50,747
You don't have to send us off.

551
00:36:50,827 --> 00:36:52,287
Have a safe journey.

552
00:36:52,605 --> 00:36:54,071
-Goodbye.
-Goodbye.

