560
00:37:29,811 --> 00:37:30,896
I see.

561
00:37:30,976 --> 00:37:32,272
You don't have to come.

562
00:37:32,352 --> 00:37:33,842
We can meet up at the restaurant.

563
00:37:34,441 --> 00:37:37,489
It doesn't matter.
We can talk at the restaurant.

564
00:37:39,748 --> 00:37:42,124
You should respect my decision
since you invited me.

565
00:37:42,204 --> 00:37:44,149
Just send me the location. I have to go.

566
00:37:53,790 --> 00:37:54,872
Where were we?

567
00:37:54,952 --> 00:37:56,198
Do you want me to tag along?

568
00:37:59,980 --> 00:38:01,179
Are you serious?

569
00:38:02,052 --> 00:38:03,480
Aren't you...

570
00:38:04,079 --> 00:38:07,014
Aren't you going to meet
the old friend you told me before?

571
00:38:07,094 --> 00:38:08,264
It's him.

572
00:38:08,680 --> 00:38:11,606
I'm asking why are you
volunteering yourself to come along?

573
00:38:17,197 --> 00:38:20,522
You still remember
what I told you before.

574
00:38:20,602 --> 00:38:23,058
Do I look like I have bad memory?

575
00:38:23,901 --> 00:38:25,173
Yes.

576
00:38:28,946 --> 00:38:31,759
You look like
you don't bother to remember things.

577
00:38:32,698 --> 00:38:33,773
Let's go.

578
00:38:33,853 --> 00:38:34,922
Let's go.

579
00:38:40,895 --> 00:38:43,714
Are you going to repeat
the same procedure every time?

580
00:38:43,794 --> 00:38:45,515
So, are you going
to argue with me as usual?

581
00:38:51,313 --> 00:38:54,359
How do you know
that call was from my old friend?

582
00:38:56,219 --> 00:38:57,354
I could tell.

583
00:38:58,259 --> 00:39:00,018
By the way, I forgot to tell you.

584
00:39:00,098 --> 00:39:02,188
Actually, we have
resolved the misunderstanding.

585
00:39:09,574 --> 00:39:11,641
We need to eat, right?

586
00:39:11,721 --> 00:39:14,309
After this meal,
all of us will become friends.

587
00:39:14,389 --> 00:39:15,637
Let's go.

588
00:39:15,717 --> 00:39:17,079
Let's go.

