591
00:39:31,494 --> 00:39:32,528
Forget it.

592
00:39:32,608 --> 00:39:34,331
I bet he hates
having someone by his side.

593
00:39:50,006 --> 00:39:51,082
Here is the lemon juice.

594
00:39:51,162 --> 00:39:52,422
Thank you.

595
00:39:55,891 --> 00:39:57,089
It's so cold.

596
00:39:57,546 --> 00:39:59,817
Stop eating. Aren't you allergic to it?

597
00:39:59,897 --> 00:40:02,719
Please bring a glass
of warm lemon juice for the lady.

598
00:40:02,799 --> 00:40:03,800
Thank you.

599
00:40:03,880 --> 00:40:06,072
