between girls is complicated.

602
00:40:15,891 --> 00:40:17,127
You know nothing.

603
00:40:17,207 --> 00:40:19,522
Fine, I don't want to know.

604
00:40:19,602 --> 00:40:22,545
I just want to know
what's wrong with her.

605
00:40:22,625 --> 00:40:24,669
She's resigned from the restaurant.

606
00:40:24,749 --> 00:40:26,048
What does she want?

607
00:40:26,728 --> 00:40:29,221
It's not about her.

608
00:40:29,625 --> 00:40:32,614
It's about you. Have you ever tried
to understand her life?

609
00:40:32,694 --> 00:40:34,847
Unlike you,
she's eager to do well in everything.

610
00:40:34,927 --> 00:40:36,996
All you care about is
managing a band for fun.

611
00:40:37,076 --> 00:40:39,901
Yes, you have a fair share of fun
but look at her.

612
00:40:39,981 --> 00:40:41,238
Ever since
she enrolled into the university,

613
00:40:41,318 --> 00:40:42,787
