636
00:42:00,233 --> 00:42:01,457
But...

637
00:42:02,444 --> 00:42:06,059
But she deserves a chance
to embrace a different future.

638
00:42:06,506 --> 00:42:09,654
Is staying in the welfare home forever
the best option she has?

639
00:42:09,734 --> 00:42:10,896
If she refuses to give it a try...

640
00:42:10,976 --> 00:42:13,040
just because
she's worried about the outcome,

641
00:42:13,120 --> 00:42:15,806
