645
00:42:24,995 --> 00:42:26,114
I...

646
00:42:27,188 --> 00:42:28,307
I...

647
00:42:39,674 --> 00:42:41,143
You're too naive.

648
00:42:41,223 --> 00:42:42,259
I...

649
00:42:49,109 --> 00:42:51,330
He's never happy with anything.
